            succinate [CPD:C00042];
            CO2 [CPD:C00011]
COMMENT     The enzyme requires Fe(II) and ascorbate. Isolated from the bacterium Streptomyces avermitilis. Part of the pathway for pentalenolactone biosynthesis.
